---
import ShareableQuote from "../../ShareableQuote.astro";
---

<section
    id="positive-specialization"
    class="relative text-[#e7e5e4] font-serif min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-12 md:py-24 border-b border-emerald-900/10 overflow-hidden"
>
    <div class="w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 flex flex-col h-full justify-center">
        <div class="text-center mb-8 md:mb-16 shrink-0">
            <span
                class="text-emerald-500/80 text-xs md:text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase block mb-4 trigo-positive-chapter"
                >El Genio</span
            >
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[#e7e5e4] mb-6">
                El Nacimiento del Genio
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-[#a8a29e] max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                <ShareableQuote
                    quote="En una tribu de cazadores, todos cazan. En una ciudad de trigo, uno cultiva y nueve pueden soñar."
                />
            </p>
        </div>

        <div
            class="flex md:grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 md:gap-8 mb-8 md:mb-12 overflow-x-auto md:overflow-visible snap-x snap-mandatory pb-4 md:pb-0 -mx-4 px-4 md:mx-0 md:px-0 no-scrollbar"
        >
            <div class="relative group min-w-[85vw] md:min-w-0 snap-center">
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-900/10 to-transparent rounded-xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1c1917] to-[#0c0a09] p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl border border-emerald-900/20 hover:border-emerald-500/40 transition-all duration-300 h-full flex flex-col justify-between"
                >
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-16 h-16 md:w-20 md:h-20 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-900/40 to-emerald-950/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
                        >
                            <svg
                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke-width="1.5"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                class="w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 text-emerald-500"
                            >
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    d="M9.75 3.104v5.714a2.25 2.25 0 01-.659 1.591L5 14.5M9.75 3.104c-.251.023-.501.05-.75.082m.75-.082a24.301 24.301 0 014.5 0m0 0v5.714c0 .597.237 1.17.659 1.591L19.8 15.3M14.25 3.104c.251.023.501.05.75.082M19.8 15.3l-1.57.393A9.065 9.065 0 0112 15a9.065 9.065 0 00-6.23-.693L5 14.5m14.8.8l1.402 1.402c1.232 1.232.65 3.318-1.067 3.611A48.309 48.309 0 0112 21c-2.773 0-5.491-.235-8.135-.687-1.718-.293-2.3-2.379-1.067-3.61L5 14.5"
                                ></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#e7e5e4] mb-2">
                                El Artesano
                            </h3>
                            <div
                                class="w-12 md:w-16 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-emerald-500/50 to-transparent mx-auto mb-4"
                            >
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-sm text-[#a8a29e] leading-relaxed">
                                Liberado de la búsqueda de comida, las manos pudieron perfeccionar
                                la arcilla, el metal y la tela. Nació el concepto de "maestro".
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pt-4 border-t border-emerald-900/20 w-full mt-4">
                        <div class="text-xs text-emerald-500/60 uppercase tracking-widest">
                            Cerámica • Metalurgia • Textiles
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative group min-w-[85vw] md:min-w-0 snap-center">
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-900/10 to-transparent rounded-xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1c1917] to-[#0c0a09] p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl border border-emerald-900/20 hover:border-emerald-500/40 transition-all duration-300 h-full flex flex-col justify-between"
                >
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-16 h-16 md:w-20 md:h-20 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-900/40 to-emerald-950/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
                        >
                            <svg
                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke-width="1.5"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                class="w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 text-emerald-500"
                            >
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    d="M9.75 3.104v5.714a2.25 2.25 0 01-.659 1.591L5 14.5M9.75 3.104c-.251.023-.501.05-.75.082m.75-.082a24.301 24.301 0 014.5 0m0 0v5.714c0 .597.237 1.17.659 1.591L19.8 15.3M14.25 3.104c.251.023.501.05.75.082M19.8 15.3l-1.57.393A9.065 9.065 0 0112 15a9.065 9.065 0 00-6.23-.693L5 14.5m14.8.8l1.402 1.402c1.232 1.232.65 3.318-1.067 3.611A48.309 48.309 0 0112 21c-2.773 0-5.491-.235-8.135-.687-1.718-.293-2.3-2.379-1.067-3.61L5 14.5"
                                ></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#e7e5e4] mb-2">
                                El Sanador
                            </h3>
                            <div
                                class="w-12 md:w-16 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-emerald-500/50 to-transparent mx-auto mb-4"
                            >
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-sm text-[#a8a29e] leading-relaxed">
                                El tiempo libre permitió la observación. Entendimos las plantas no
                                solo como comida, sino como medicina. Nació la farmacología.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pt-4 border-t border-emerald-900/20 w-full mt-4">
                        <div class="text-xs text-emerald-500/60 uppercase tracking-widest">
                            Herbolaria • Cirugía • Diagnóstico
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative group min-w-[85vw] md:min-w-0 snap-center">
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-900/10 to-transparent rounded-xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1c1917] to-[#0c0a09] p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl border border-emerald-900/20 hover:border-emerald-500/40 transition-all duration-300 h-full flex flex-col justify-between"
                >
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center space-y-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-16 h-16 md:w-20 md:h-20 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-900/40 to-emerald-950/20 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
                        >
                            <svg
                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke-width="1.5"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                class="w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 text-emerald-500"
                            >
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    d="M11.48 3.499a.562.562 0 011.04 0l2.125 5.111a.563.563 0 00.475.345l5.518.442c.499.04.701.663.321.988l-4.204 3.602a.563.563 0 00-.182.557l1.285 5.385a.562.562 0 01-.84.61l-4.725-2.885a.563.563 0 00-.586 0L6.982 20.54a.562.562 0 01-.84-.61l1.285-5.386a.562.562 0 00-.182-.557l-4.204-3.602a.563.563 0 01.321-.988l5.518-.442a.563.563 0 00.475-.345L11.48 3.5z"
                                ></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-[#e7e5e4] mb-2">
                                El Astrónomo
                            </h3>
                            <div
                                class="w-12 md:w-16 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-emerald-500/50 to-transparent mx-auto mb-4"
                            >
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-sm text-[#a8a29e] leading-relaxed">
                                Necesitábamos predecir las cosechas. Así que miramos arriba y
                                mapeamos las estrellas. Inventamos el calendario y las matemáticas.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pt-4 border-t border-emerald-900/20 w-full mt-4">
                        <div class="text-xs text-emerald-500/60 uppercase tracking-widest">
                            Astronomía • Calendario • Geometría
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto w-full shrink-0">
            <div
                class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-900/5 via-emerald-500/10 to-emerald-900/5 blur-2xl"
            >
            </div>
            <div
                class="relative bg-[#0c0a09] border border-emerald-900/30 rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 text-center"
            >
                <div
                    class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6 md:gap-12 mb-4 md:mb-6"
                >
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-stone-600 mb-2">100%</div>
                        <div class="text-xs text-[#a8a29e] uppercase tracking-wider">Cazadores</div>
                        <div class="text-xs text-stone-700 mt-1">Antes del trigo</div>
                    </div>
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        class="w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 text-emerald-500/50 rotate-90 md:rotate-0"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-emerald-500 mb-2">10%</div>
                        <div class="text-xs text-[#a8a29e] uppercase tracking-wider">
                            Agricultores
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-xs text-emerald-700 mt-1">Después del trigo</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-[#78716c] max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    El excedente liberó al 90% de la población para dedicarse a la innovación, el
                    arte y la ciencia. Por primera vez, la humanidad pudo especializarse.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
